{"word":"H994 - בִּי - bîy - bee - Alas","slug":"H994","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בִּי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Alas"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D9; - b&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>bee</i><p/>Perhaps from <a href=\"#/H1158\">H1158</a> (in the sense of <i>asking</i>); properly a <i>request</i>; used only adverbially (always with &ldquo;my Lord&rdquo;); <i>Oh that</i>!; <i>with leave</i>, or <i>if it please: - </i>alas, O, oh."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H15\">H15</a>"}]}